data.description: Inside the master planned community of Wingfield Springs, just minutes from Red Hawk Country Club, this spacious 5 bedroom home has been meticulously well taken care of. With solar panels to reduce your monthly utility bills, electric car charging, and a modern upgraded interior, this home is an absolute gem! One full bedroom and bath on the main floor. Enjoy an open living space with luxury vinyl plank flooring. The kitchen is an entertainer's dream with granite countertops, a large island, pantry and newer appliances as the home was just built in 2019. Upstairs you'll find a loft for extra gathering or play space. The spacious primary bedroom includes a walk-in closet and dual sinks, tub & shower. Outside you'll find professional landscaping with a covered patio, pavered side yard and beautiful views, just a short walk away from all the amenities Wingfield Springs has to offer! Playset in the backyard stays with the property.
